rows.label: bf11450100_0010
rows.name: I haven't seen him since.

rows.label: bf11450100_0020
rows.name:
A little while later,
I heard he'd climbed the World Tree.

rows.label: bf11450100_0030
rows.name: And he returned with the word of God.

rows.label: bf11450100_0040
rows.name: That being...

rows.label: bf11450100_0050
rows.name: The Heaven's Holy Grail, Metsu.

rows.label: bf11450100_0060
rows.name: But is this really His word?

rows.label: bf11450100_0070
rows.name: Is this salvation from God?

rows.label: bf11450100_0080
rows.name:
There's no way something like this
could be called salvation.

rows.label: bf11450100_0085
rows.name: This is his desire...

rows.label: bf11450100_0090
rows.name: No, it is his despair.

rows.label: bf11450100_0100
rows.name: Despair...?

rows.label: bf11450100_0110
rows.name: What about you? You come from the same root.

rows.label: bf11450100_0120
rows.name: I have no clue what you're talking about.

rows.label: bf11450100_0130
rows.name:
He woke me up,
so I'm just sticking with him. That's it.

rows.label: bf11450100_0140
rows.name:
I don't care about this world's
origins or its future.

rows.label: bf11450100_0150
rows.name: Not even Metsu?

rows.label: bf11450100_0160
rows.name: I don't give a damn what he's thinking.

rows.label: bf11450100_0165
rows.name: I've never even met the guy.

rows.label: bf11450100_0170
rows.name: Don't get the wrong idea.

rows.label: bf11450100_0175
rows.name: Despite how she acts, she's a good kid.

rows.label: bf11450100_0180
rows.name: What's with that tone?

rows.label: bf11450100_0185
rows.name: Since when are you my guardian?

rows.label: bf11450100_0190
rows.name: Hahaha, what's the big deal?

rows.label: bf11450100_0195
rows.name: I am paying your food bills, after all.

rows.label: bf11450100_0200
rows.name: Huh?

rows.label: bf11450100_0210
rows.name:
Those Cloud Sea Crab Cream Croquettes
last night were good, right?

rows.label: bf11450100_0220
rows.name: Although, six of them was probably overkill.

rows.label: bf11450100_0230
rows.name: H-hey! You had to bring that up now?!

rows.label: bf11450100_0240
rows.name: You're going to get fat if you keep that up.

rows.label: bf11450100_0250
rows.name: I'm a Blade, I can't get fat!

rows.label: bf11450100_0260
rows.name: Hey!

rows.label: bf11450100_0270
rows.name: I can pinch it with no problem.

rows.label: bf11450100_0275
rows.name: This is bad.

rows.label: bf11450100_0280
rows.name: You little...!

rows.label: bf11450100_0290
rows.name:
Hehe! Chubby, chubby!
The Heaven's Holy Grail is chubby!

rows.label: bf11450100_0300
rows.name: Get back here, Milt!

rows.label: bf11450100_0310
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]Heh.

rows.label: bf11450100_0320
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?

rows.label: bf11450100_0330
rows.name: You know... if God is real,

rows.label: bf11450100_0340
rows.name: I'd like to meet him.

rows.label: bf11450100_0350
rows.name: Salvation...
